<div
  style="
    width: 100%;
    padding-top: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
    border: 3px solid #c2c2c2;
    background-color: #ffffff;
  "
>
  <div style="width: 90%; margin: 0 auto">
    <h3 style="margin-left: 20px; padding: 0">안녕하세요. 추천대출입니다.</h3>

    <ul>
      <li style="padding-bottom: 10px">
        아이디와 비밀번호 정보를 보내드립니다.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <div
      style="
        background-color: rgba(212, 212, 212);
        border: 1px sold gray;
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 5px 20px;
      "
    >
      <p style="font-weight: bold">
        <span>아이디:</span>
        <span style="color: rgba(252, 93, 8)"><%= locals.identity %></span>
      </p>

      <p style="font-weight: bold">
        <span>비밀번호:</span>
        <span style="color: rgba(252, 93, 8)"><%= locals.password %></span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
